    "On the Mac: Settings → API tokens → Mint token (Read + write). Permanent until you revoke it.": {
      "comment": "A description of how to generate an API token for use with Splynek.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "pt-PT": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No Mac: Definições → Tokens de API → Criar token (Leitura + escrita). Permanente até o revogares."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "En el Mac: Ajustes → Tokens de API → Crear token (Lectura + escritura). Permanente hasta que lo revoques."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sur le Mac : Réglages → Jetons d'API → Créer un jeton (Lecture + écriture). Permanent jusqu'à révocation."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Am Mac: Einstellungen → API-Tokens → Token erstellen (Lesen + schreiben). Bleibt bestehen, bis Sie ihn widerrufen."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sul Mac: Impostazioni → Token API → Crea token (Lettura + scrittura). Permanente fino a quando non lo revochi."
          }
        }
      }
    },
